{"tid":6481,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［箍牙］有冇巴絲可以推介牙醫","createTime":"2016-11-27T11:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T14:28:37.000Z","uid":8234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"770ab309abc1a1d336bf0a0ae8b942e56e9c9eac","tid":6481,"uid":8234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:29:23.000Z","msg":"想搵間價錢合理，最好箍傳統收二萬幾至三萬蚊左右，又可以分期既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我仲係學生，想箍牙好耐不過唔想用屋企人錢，要返part time逐個月比啲<br />\n所以希望搵間平又可以分期既牙醫診所（最好係旺角佐敦嗰頭，或者元朗都可以）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知應該開係邊個台，如果開錯請屌得輕手啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d269e06fe331418f4fb8ed5dea75c270bd5eceb8","tid":6481,"uid":8234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:55:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cd3ded02043dd765a5477386c847b7b1b2e1d424","tid":6481,"uid":16108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:59:12.000Z","msg":"有朋友係天水圍箍<br />\n好似2萬8 <br />\n但要兩個禮拜覆一次診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb646b76b0e8dd70745acd819134f66b05c17a07","tid":6481,"uid":8234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有朋友係天水圍箍<br />\n好似2萬8 <br />\n但要兩個禮拜覆一次診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下佢箍左幾耐，同埋箍成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08dce991cb21281c0e0241a703b4837f7c5738a","tid":6481,"uid":16108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"仲有個朋友好似係旺角箍 <br />\n好似三萬幾"},{"pid":"6566224fcd31596407017cc5b541da74fc9382f8","tid":6481,"uid":16108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有朋友係天水圍箍<br />\n好似2萬8 <br />\n但要兩個禮拜覆一次診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下佢箍左幾耐，同埋箍成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢近排先箍 大概一個月到 <br />\n要箍兩年 箍左一個月無咩大變化 <br />\n個人仲好似肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b47cb3d396c7a9bc071171c68852d63f7b3293","tid":6481,"uid":8234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有朋友係天水圍箍<br />\n好似2萬8 <br />\n但要兩個禮拜覆一次診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下佢箍左幾耐，同埋箍成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢近排先箍 大概一個月到 <br />\n要箍兩年 箍左一個月無咩大變化 <br />\n個人仲好似肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係有冇話個醫生細唔細心嗰啲，我朋友次次換箍都比個醫生整到流晒血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw可唔可以講下天水圍同旺角嗰間係咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11a1d2ffffb28f2aba50e96f4203823d5c6370d","tid":6481,"uid":16108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:18:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有朋友係天水圍箍<br />\n好似2萬8 <br />\n但要兩個禮拜覆一次診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下佢箍左幾耐，同埋箍成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢近排先箍 大概一個月到 <br />\n要箍兩年 箍左一個月無咩大變化 <br />\n個人仲好似肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係有冇話個醫生細唔細心嗰啲，我朋友次次換箍都比個醫生整到流晒血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw可唔可以講下天水圍同旺角嗰間係咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n天水圍個間係天耀 佢話淨係記得個醫生叫張魷卓<br />\n旺角個間唔係好清楚 <br />\n佢話唔會搞到流晒血 但mock牙真係好痛 <br />\n（啱啱打比佢問）<img s